description:
Hi;

Contained is my novel _Crown the Jester_, which is also available on Amazon and the B&amp;N Nook store.

If people want to pay for it that is fine; if they want to download it via torrent that is also fine.

I am not a professional writer, though I have been paid real money for poems by magazines (not much.)(  This is my first novel.

Converted more or less by Calibre.

You can read about it here:
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://crownthejester.com&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://crownthejester.com&lt;/a&gt;

Crown the Jester tells the story of the first 100 days of Frank Sinatra's presidency, in the summer of 1963. The Rat Pack has taken over the Cabinet, Joe DiMaggio is in prison, Nixon's head is in the clouds, and Marilyn Monroe's on the lam. If only she'd been born with a hymen!
